# Polynomials

```julia
using Plots
using CalculusWithJulia
```

```julia
a, b, c = symbols("a, b, c")

x = symbols("x", real = true)
```

```julia
p = -16x^2 + 100

typeof(p)

quad = a*x^2 + b*x + c
```

```julia
sin(a*(x - b*pi) + c)

quad + quad^2 - quad^3
```

```julia
p = -16x^2 + 100
p(p => (x-1)^2)

y = p(x => 2)

p(4)
```

```julia
@vars a b c E F
p = a*x^2 + b*x + c
p(x => x-E) + F

expand(p(x => x-E) + F)
```

```julia
p = -16x^2 + 100
y = p(2)
N(y)

N(PI, 60)
```

